1. 
postorder: root node start from the end of the postorder array

preorder: root node start from the start of the preorder array

2. fort this kind fo questions, the logic is:

    a. Find the root node
    b. Recursively build the right and left tree

Note:
a. subtree size calculation to able to determine the next root of subtree
    inOrderEnd - inOrderRoot = the size of right subtree
    inOrderRoot - inOrderStart = the size of left subtree